617
00:28:50,428 --> 00:28:52,362
That's better!

618
00:28:54,232 --> 00:28:56,132
Will dinner be good?

619
00:28:56,167 --> 00:28:57,691
l hope so!

620
00:28:57,736 --> 00:29:00,068
