a surprise for you.

622
00:29:03,341 --> 00:29:04,899
Why?

623
00:29:04,943 --> 00:29:06,604
lmportant news.

624
00:29:06,644 --> 00:29:08,475
Our fortune increased
tenfold, perhaps.

625
00:29:08,513 --> 00:29:10,674
-Lovely!
-Once our overseas guest tonight

626
